Sam Fox, 56, married her fiancée Linda Olsen, on Saturday after following their engagement. The former Celebrity Big Brother contestant chose a show-stopping strapless bridal gown to celebrate with her loved ones in Epping Forest, Essex. Her new wife opted for a floor-length wedding dress, with both brides opting for short trains and veils. The happy couple matched make-up looks featuring a red lip and a smokey eye in earthy tones, as well as a half-up hairstyle.